<l>viṇṇeṉa varūuṅ kāyap peyarvayi</l>
<l>ṉuṇmaiyu murittē yatteṉ cāriyai</l>
<l>ceyyuṇ maruṅkiṟ ṟoḻilvaru kālai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the noun <foreign xml:lang="ta">viṇ</foreign> which denotes sky<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">kāyam,</foreign> i.e. <foreign xml:lang="ta">ākāyam &lt;</foreign> Skt. <foreign xml:lang="sa">ākāsa.</foreign></note></l>
<l>occurs in poetry [and] is followed by verb,</l>
<l>it is proper that the empty morph <foreign xml:lang="ta">attu</foreign> be inserted.<note place="foot">e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">viṇṇakattuk koṭkum.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
